        "orig": "Women's    Polytechnic  was  established  as the  first  Institute  of  its  kind  for  promoting technical education to the women of Tripura. Women's Polytechnic was established in the year 2003 with the pioneering branch of Information Technology (IT) approved by AICTE. In 2004, two additional new branches namely, Medical Lab Technology (MLT) and Fashion Technology (FT) were incorporated. In 2011, Electronics  and  Telecommunication  (ETCE) branch was introduced. It is located about 9 km  approximately  far  from  the  capital  city Agartala.",
